<h3>***Help***</h3>
<div class="postmsg">
<p>Hi all,</p><p>I have just installed the latest full version of Parrot OS onto my new Thinkpad however,</p><p>The scaling of the screen looks really small... I mean... Really small. I have a 2560x1440 screen and I am not sure if that makes a difference?</p><p>I have tried changing the resolution, but that just makes it even worse... Help?</p><p>Thanks,</p><p>####<br/>#IDE#<br/>####</p>
</div>
</div>
